{
  "stem": "19441.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 338.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they said, we heard what is your fate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you lie down, and we will wash all the toilets for you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If somebody will come, one from us will watch, and then you quickly get up, and-- so that, that you are working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Quickly I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I sat on the toilet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Blockfuhrer who was friend of the other SS man, who told him that I did the painting this time for the good of the SS too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they been friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he heard that-- what happened to me-- so he had a certain with the other-- they been friends-- to, to save me from it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because seven days I couldn't manage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There-- so many toilets, and all night standing, then the roll call, then again the roll call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was seven days standing, and I was seven day doing toilets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not I did it-- the men did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the last day, he arrived and took me straightaway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did do the punishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was not a block of-- like the Jewish women was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a wooden barrack, because they was mostly non-Jewish women who worked in the offices and in the establishment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were used to it, you know, to do-- like when it was the counting, they did all the businesses, because they been the [NON-ENGLISH], you know-- the high society.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I came there, I said, look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here-- he brought me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, when he went, I didn't ask to be your blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one thing I ask you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I will do everything possible to help you, but you have to listen to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
